{"tid":1982387,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"疫症下，汽車戲院的復興","createTime":"2020-04-21T07:37:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-21T08:11:16.000Z","uid":4260,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"020462db74f0e15a9efb59f3031b744c97eb847b","tid":1982387,"uid":4260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T07:37:10.000Z","msg":"疫症肆虐全球，全球電影業大受打擊。全世界影展無不宣告延期，新電影大多推遲上映時間，戲院也被視作高危場所，包括香港等多地政府勒令關閉&mdash;&mdash;但在美歐韓，本已碩果僅存的「汽車戲院」（Drive-in theater），卻久旱逢雨般復興起來。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>安全地在戶外看電影</strong><br />\n<br />\n疫情之下，看電影，最好是安坐家中串流，或者播碟，看電影台。畢竟，不接觸人，就不會感染。<br />\n<br />\n但在美國、歐洲、南韓，汽車戲院亦是種相較安全的選擇：駕車駛入放映埸地，車頭對正大銀幕，用車內無線電接收音效，調好車椅，一家大小即可與坐在鄰近觀眾一起各自在車內觀賞電影，同時不違保持社交距離的金科玉律。<br />\n<br />\n是故，汽車戲院在疫情底下，成了怕受感染、但又想出門約會的人的好去處。在南韓首爾，有人不惜排隊兩小時，購買周末汽車戲院放映的門票。在德國埃森市，當地汽車戲院只在網上發售門票，現場不賣小食，每架車僅限兩位成人觀眾，但周末放映的門票都全部售罄。在美國，以往慣於夏季才會營業的汽車戲院也看準商機，紛紛提早回歸。據報，英國也有公司正積極考慮復興戶外汽車戲院。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.mpweekly.com/culture/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/000-1q972t-20200402053954.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mpweekly.com%2Fculture%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F04%2F000-1q972t-20200402053954.jpg&h=a0c0d27f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n在德國西部埃森市，汽車戲院的銀幕在開場前教觀眾如何在車內收聽電影聲音。<br />\n<br />\n無論是在何處，近年無人問津的汽車戲院，營業額均節節上升。美國德州Showboat汽車戲院的東主Andrew Thomas接受CNBC訪問時說，「人們會來，是因為他們想找那種正常狀態的感覺。」在不正常的日子，總令人懷緬舊日的美好，想尋回所謂正常生活的平凡感。<br />\n<br />\n於是，一個幾乎已成過去的產業，在人心惶惶的時間，暫時重獲新生。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>汽車戲院的發源</strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.mpweekly.com/culture/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/first-drive-in-theater-camden-nj-1933-20200402053708.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mpweekly.com%2Fculture%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F04%2Ffirst-drive-in-theater-camden-nj-1933-20200402053708.jpg&h=c4001e17&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n一九三三年，首間汽車戲院在美國新澤西州肯頓市（Camden）面世。<br />\n<br />\n汽車戲院最早於一九三〇年代初在美國新澤西州問世，由商人Richard Hollingshead創立。有指，他會萌生汽車戲院的念頭，是因為母親坐不慣在傳統戲院中坐不慣，於是他就構思如何能讓觀眾可以在戶外，舒適地坐在私家車中看電影。<br />\n<br />\n最初，他先在家門前的車路做實驗，在自己的車頂放部柯達放映機，把屏幕釘在幾棵樹上，在幕後放音響，看看效果。一九三三年，他將這「汽車戲院」的設計申請專利，並付諸實現。第一部在Hollingshead的汽車戲院放的電影，是亞多富文殊（Adolphe Menjou）主演的《Two White Arms》（1932）。<br />\n<br />\n在一九五〇至六〇年代，正值嬰兒潮、私家車平民化的時期，汽車戲院迎來了它的黃金年代，成為美國的五〇年代的文化標籤之一。相較室內戲院便宜，容許家長看顧孩子之餘看電影娛樂的汽車戲院，深受一般大眾家庭愛戴。當其時，美國全國有超過四千間汽車戲院，最大型的汽車戲院，車位可達二千多個。但到了七〇年代，電視機、錄影帶大行其道，一家大小足不出戶就可看電影，汽車戲院的生意便自然的持續下滑，昔日光輝也無以復返。<br />\n<br />\n如今，全美只剩下三百多間汽車戲院仍然經營，賣懷舊情懷，特地去汽車戲院看電影的觀眾少之又少。<br />\n<br />\n但又有誰可料到，疫症的爆發，竟為汽車戲院帶來一場的小復興？汽車戲院的復興可能是暫時的，但人們在疫情下仍堅持找安全的方法，出家門外看電影，展露的，除了是人與外界接觸的恆久渴求，更是那種與羣眾一起觀影時、無可代替的體驗之重要。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.mpweekly.com/culture/汽車戲院-電影-疫症-143152\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mpweekly.com%2Fculture%2F%E6%B1%BD%E8%BB%8A%E6%88%B2%E9%99%A2-%E9%9B%BB%E5%BD%B1-%E7%96%AB%E7%97%87-143152&d=ncMleFGONnlHWKA8FqKBiYnGVh3W70%2FpCcVRRx8QUyg%3D&h=db28815e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.mpweekly.com/culture/汽車戲院-電影-疫症-143152</a>"},{"pid":"a957bead4a5fb3cf6963b6a683b583f2fc08321e","tid":1982387,"uid":3987,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T07:38:44.000Z","msg":"香港奴隸做唔到既野<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ddfa96baad4b4849f193fdfeb4cb93ab15661c7a","tid":1982387,"uid":201604,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T07:39:41.000Z","msg":"香港人又冇車又冇地"},{"pid":"75a6c6e498ec177cec262d16691abd5e30f41fe1","tid":1982387,"uid":313584,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T07:47:36.000Z","msg":"香港以前有㗎<br />\n不過又係做唔住"},{"pid":"c532b38be0c1586422467179c8a71ae99bb8fad5","tid":1982387,"uid":4260,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T07:48:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.mpweekly.com/culture/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/000-1q315s-20200402052354.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mpweekly.com%2Fculture%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F04%2F000-1q315s-20200402052354.jpg&h=1a7538da&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n在首爾的汽車戲院，有上百架車輛齊集一起，人們在車內觀賞放映。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.mpweekly.com/culture/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/000-1q315x-20200402052356.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mpweekly.com%2Fculture%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F04%2F000-1q315x-20200402052356.jpg&h=2e0c45bc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n駕車到汽車戲院看電影，成為了疫情下戀人在戶外安全約會的活動。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.mpweekly.com/culture/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/000-1q3160-20200402054841.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mpweekly.com%2Fculture%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F04%2F000-1q3160-20200402054841.jpg&h=7e8a9a6c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n高空下拍攝的一間首爾汽車戲院，場內有兩個大銀幕同時做放映。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.mpweekly.com/culture/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/000-1q972h-20200402052808.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mpweekly.com%2Fculture%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F04%2F000-1q972h-20200402052808.jpg&h=92235278&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n到汽車戲院看電影是在德國埃森市市民當前的熱門周末娛樂<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.mpweekly.com/culture/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/000-1q972z-20200402052410.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mpweekly.com%2Fculture%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F04%2F000-1q972z-20200402052410.jpg&h=a065e8a5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n德國埃森市的汽車戲院使用電影門票，事先需在網上購票<br />\n<br />\n在美國猶他州，天氣嚴寒，但不少一家大小會到汽車戲院看電影。見室內戲院關閉，當地汽車戲院決定提早營業<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.mpweekly.com/culture/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/063-1208471796-20200402052419.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mpweekly.com%2Fculture%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F04%2F063-1208471796-20200402052419.jpg&h=36023230&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n在美國猶他州的汽車戲院，一家五口全部坐在車頭，等待電影開場。"},{"pid":"8d87335d3a2ea658c2f118f02307460419b2cb70","tid":1982387,"uid":167931,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T07:50:14.000Z","msg":"Good afternoon sir"},{"pid":"9c31b8f781ce2167d6dc621dd5eafcb0a7d788fe","tid":1982387,"uid":236891,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T07:50:50.000Z","msg":"有netflix 都唔洗要呢d"},{"pid":"0718b1975876dac12b6ab4835d22336ed7e8b82d","tid":1982387,"uid":80396,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"9c31b8f781ce2167d6dc621dd5eafcb0a7d788fe","tid":1982387,"uid":236891,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T07:50:50.000Z","msg":"有netflix 都唔洗要呢d"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T07:55:44.000Z","msg":"又唔係既，兩種FEEL黎。"},{"pid":"45cfb4af46679107e68ef9852783fc690eaba358","tid":1982387,"uid":85774,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T07:56:14.000Z","msg":"香港人一定唔得  為左個位會有交通意外"},{"pid":"197afc6025173dc2827495bae949f4aa5dadf6ee","tid":1982387,"uid":228995,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T08:02:50.000Z","msg":"睇完就順便去motel?"},{"pid":"317801139427f68032dc41b428e76e6dff362682","tid":1982387,"uid":33868,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T08:03:30.000Z","msg":"番屋企開個projector睇咪得"},{"pid":"4987269b69132f4330401839c5058e37eb63643c","tid":1982387,"uid":33868,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T08:04:13.000Z","msg":"以前西九都有"},{"pid":"8d9193b071b496087f1850cc42cfbcdc7c39798a","tid":1982387,"uid":104804,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0718b1975876dac12b6ab4835d22336ed7e8b82d","tid":1982387,"uid":80396,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"9c31b8f781ce2167d6dc621dd5eafcb0a7d788fe","tid":1982387,"uid":236891,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T07:50:50.000Z","msg":"有netflix 都唔洗要呢d"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T07:55:44.000Z","msg":"又唔係既，兩種FEEL黎。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T08:07:58.000Z","msg":"屋企有間房set好都ok既"},{"pid":"60228350e9bb6579c682418f5c9c96ca6ccb81b9","tid":1982387,"uid":75072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T0